name: #1-Kitchy
description:
#1-Kitchy is the first and original watercolour sketch of the series: Kitty Verse. Kitchy was sketched along with Kitchy's friends. Watercolours were added, the paper used is linen. Kitchy is the "Goddess" of Kitty Verse. Should you acquire this NFT creation, the new owner will receive a gift of the original "Kitchy" watercolour painting framed and signed.
Kitchy was created by using I-Movie, Keynote, Glitchy Psychedelic Camera VHS, l Motion Leap by Light Tricks  Music in these videos if any provided by JBR Visuals.
Love and Light, 
JBR

2160 x 2160
Codecs - H.264 
No music, only glitch affects used.
